window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Are you a sociopath and dissatisfied with your life? Don't know what to do about it or where to begin?</p> <p>In that case, we have the solution.</p> <p>Congratulations! A system has come to your world. Half of you will die and become zombies, while the other half must try to survive, if they can.</p> <p>Rejoice, sociopath, this world is made for you. Good luck!</p>"; 
